article_title: Are You Insured? Obamacare Deadline Quickly Approaching

article_metadata.author: Kelly Phillips Erb

og.description: Are you insured? If you're not insured, the deadline to enroll in health care coverage through the Marketplace is quickly approaching. Mark your calendar: the last day to make a change (and avoid paying tax for failure to obtain coverage) is February 15.
